Package: grainsizeR
Type: Package
Title: Sediment Grain-Size Analysis Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Ching-Sung G.",
           family = "Chang",
           email = "cschang.bt10@nycu.edu.tw",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Read, validate, summarize, and plot sediment grain-size
    distributions. The package supports long and wide retained-size inputs,
    cumulative curves, D-values, percent-finer interpolation, grain-size
    statistics, particle-size fractions, GRADISTAT/G2Sd-style analysis
    workflows, major texture classification, texture ternary plots, and
    user-supplied texture polygon classification workflows.
